definitions.definition: A people who live predominantly in the mountainous regions of China, Vietnam, Laos, and Thailand, and (in diaspora ) around the world.

main_definition: A people who live predominantly in the mountainous regions of China, Vietnam, Laos, and Thailand, and (in diaspora ) around the world.

definitions.definition: The lect spoken by these people, which is a cluster of a large number of lects which are sometimes considered dialects and sometimes separate languages.

main_definition: The lect spoken by these people, which is a cluster of a large number of lects which are sometimes considered dialects and sometimes separate languages.
